<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id76f5ae5a-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s47–4"><num value="47–4">§ 47–4.</num><heading> Agreements to effectuate leases</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of the Interior may enter into agreements with other Federal agencies and with any concessioner or its successor in order to effectuate the purposes of sections 47–2 to 47–6 of this title.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id76f5ae5b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/90/409/s3">Pub. L. 90–409, § 3</ref>, formerly § 2, <date date="1968-07-21">July 21, 1968</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/82/393">82 Stat. 393</ref>; renumbered § 3, <ref href="/us/pl/99/542/s1/4">Pub. L. 99–542, § 1(4)</ref>, <date date="1986-10-27">Oct. 27, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/3037">100 Stat. 3037</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id76f5ae5c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id76f5ae5d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id76f5ae5e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s47–2/b">section 47–2(b) of this title</ref> prior to renumbering by <ref href="/us/pl/99/542">Pub. L. 99–542</ref>.</p>
</note>
